main_body:
Member States shall ensure that:
(a) authorisations for plant protection products containing azocyclotin, cyhexatin and thidiazuron are withdrawn by 4 October 2008;
(b) from 5 April 2008 no authorisations for plant protection products containing azocyclotin, cyhexatin and thidiazuron are granted or renewed under the derogation provided for in Article 8(2) of Directive 91/414/EEC.
